tus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n或者share以下既圖去twitter<br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n3. 叫埋外國人一齊Report俾WhatsApp聽，增加noise<br />\n尾數雙數先係business，單數係正常account<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係兩種acc都違反晒terms of service！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n班狗想分散投資，不過我地要port到佢一條不留！<br />\n<br />\n祝大家舉報愉快<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yxr6aC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yxr6aC.jpg&h=ab2b926e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZqeBKbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZqeBKbL.jpg&h=93c8393e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd8b30564f85ff34104d09aefb9a7d4310512bd5","tid":1560544,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}